summaries.short: As they start settling into college life, first-year suite mates Kimberly, Bela, Leighton, and Whitney navigate relationships, extracurriculars, and culture shock. Later, the girls hit an exclusive party to blow off some steam.
summaries.full: After saying goodbye to their parents, first-year suite mates Kimberly, Bela, Leighton, and Whitney begin adjusting to college life. While Leighton falls out with her high school friends, Whitney clashes with a teammate, Kimberly struggles with culture shock, and Bela guns for a coveted spot on the school’s comedy magazine, the Catullan. Later, the girls head to an exclusive party to blow off some steam.

Disappointed by a tame start to the school year, Bela coaxes Kimberly into attending a naked party. Meanwhile, Whitney confronts Coach Dalton about his deception and attempts to broker peace with her soccer rival.
